Texts.Eng: A collection of standard gardening tools.

Texts.Chs: 锄头，铲子，耙子，扫帚。。。哦，嘿！连一根水管都没有！
Texts.Eng: A hoe, a shovel, a rake, a broom... oh hey! Even a hose!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人不需要愚蠢的工具来种植东西！
Texts.Eng: Floran doesn't need ssstupid tools to grow things!

Texts.Chs: 这似乎是一套园艺工具。
Texts.Eng: It appears to be a collection of garden tools.

Texts.Chs: 没有什么比照料花园更让我安心的了。这是猿族平民为数不多的安慰之一。
Texts.Eng: Nothing puts me at ease like tending a garden. It's one of the few comforts Apex civilians have left.

Texts.Chs: 任何一个园艺专家都可以使用的工具。
Texts.Eng: The tools of the trade for any green thumb.

Texts.Chs: 这些工具可能会加倍用于农活。
Texts.Eng: These here tools could probably double for farm work.

Texts.Chs: 有了这些工具，我确信我能造出一座宏伟的花园。
Texts.Eng: With these tools at hand, I'm certain I could make a magnificent garden.
